[27/10/2019 04:05:39] <font color="#ffff00">No.</font>
[27/10/2019 04:05:42] <font color="#ffff00">Estas naranjas parten</font>
[27/10/2019 04:05:42] <font color="#ffff00">para satisfacer</font>
